summary:
Some ECE Presets for Enhanced Character Edit

This is only for those who know what they are doing and remember to back up there existing CME save folder.
descriptionHtml:
Attention please, the second main file is no use for ECE users, I perfer ECE myself but Race Menu is undeniably more powerful and a few requests came for some of my characters, I therefore used a utility from the nexus called Chargen Export to transfere two of my characters heads which are they usable for making Race Menu presets which it did.

 So the second main file is only for RACEMENU users, I am staying with ECE myself despite this and am slowly getting more skilled at using the Vertex editing, I actually started off with RACEMENU a few years ago but liked the characters being created by ECE users more and for me there are really only two areas which ECE need's to match it and they are OVERLAY function for body tattoo's, warpaint's etc and HD head compatibility but I can live without that for now.

********

 I have uploaded a new preset set as preset 5 for ECE users this has new requirement's and may be more compatible.

 Race Nord

 Fair Skin by HHaley

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?

 Numbenumes Eyebrow's Maro

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7625/?

 XPMS using the slightly older 250 version as he has now dropped ECE support

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800/? (Install the ECE slider plugins)

 ECE by TKTK1

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/? (no sunken)

 With Rans plugin

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35713/?

 And these mod's everyone should have even if they use replacement hair.
 Better vanilla hair mesh's

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28491/?

 And some texture's to go with them.
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/4307/?
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3397/?

 This is my own current character but she is open source so do whatever you want.

*********

 Only for those who know what they are doing, Do not attempt to install with NMM this is not a mod just a set of character presets (ALL BUT ONE ARE FEMALE)
 I have shared the three I uploaded a while ago before taking it down as I only intended that for a short time and in this folder I have put another folder for you to experiment with my current presets, not all are any good but some are ok.
 Remember they will definitely look different on your computer, I am using XP32 Maximum Skeleton on Sevenbase Bombshell body so the body's may look odd without it and the skin, eye's, hair, brows, tattoo's etc are dependant upon what you have installed so they are really only any good for you to tinker with to your own satisfaction and only if you like my aesthetics as we all have different view's and as the old saying goes Beauty is in the eye of the beholder (they also say love is blind which explains a lot but I don't actually believe that).

 Best of luck

 I will probably delete these in a couple of day's or a week or so but may leave it up.
